## How to use

- Requires `semantic_id`, `title`, `category`, `complexity`, `content`; optional `requires`, `enables`, `tags`.
- After adding content on a writable host, call `chia_knowledge_rebuild_reindex` so search/FTS sees it.
- Avoid on read-only production unless deployment is known writable.

## Project

Chia graph tools do **not** take `project`.
